{"title":"板猪的难题","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1347","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span> Farmer lunar<span style=\"\">给她的宠物板猪出了一道难题</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>    求  <span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">(dx^2+2x+1)^k </span><span style=\"\">展开后 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">a1*x^2k+a2*x^(2k-1)+a3*x^(2k-2)....a(2k+1)*x^0</span><span style=\"\">中</span></span></p>\n<p><span>系数 <span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">a1+a2+a3+a4..a(2*k+1) </span><span style=\"\">的和 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">(</span><span style=\"\">这里</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">d,k</span><span style=\"\">已给出</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">);</span></span></p>\n<p><span>    没算出板猪就不能吃饭喽<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">!</span></span></p>\n<p><span>大家一定是有爱心的人吧<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">!</span><span style=\"\">快来帮助板猪吧</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">!</span></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span> </span><span> 一行<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">,</span><span style=\"\">两个整数</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">d,k,</span><span style=\"\">用空格隔开</span></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\"><span>a1+a2+a3+a4..a(2*k+1)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的和</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;输出后<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">位不足补</span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">0</span></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>1 2</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>【样例解释】</span></p>\n<p><span>将 <span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">d=1 k=2 </span><span style=\"\">代入得</span></span></p>\n<p><span>(x^2+2x+1)^2=x^4+4*x^3+6*x^2+4*x+1</span></p>\n<p><span>则<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">1+4+6+4+1=16</span></span></p>\n<p><span>【数据规模】 </span></p>\n<p><span>30% <span style=\"\">数据 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">k&lt;=20</span></span></p>\n<p><span>80% <span style=\"\">数据 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">k&lt;=1000</span></span></p>\n<p><span>100% <span style=\"\">数据 </span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">d&lt;=100  k&lt;=1000000  </span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}